cartProducts : [],\n    tags : [],\n    slotCallback : null,\n    isCheckout : false,\n    mobileTags : {width: true, pixelRatio: true},\n    sliderElementId : 'kairion_slideshow_rotator',\n    sliderContent : '',\n\n    addPageType : function(pageType){\n        this.pageType = pageType;\n    },\n\n    addJsonProduct : function(jsonFormatedProductData){\n        if (jsonFormatedProductData !== null\n            && typeof jsonFormatedProductData === 'object')\n                 this.products.push(jsonFormatedProductData);\n    },\n\n    addProducts : function(jsonFormatedProductDataArray){\n        for (var i in jsonFormatedProductDataArray)\n        {\n            this.addJsonProduct(jsonFormatedProductDataArray[i]);\n        }\n    },\n\n    addSlot : function(slotName, containerName){\n        this.slots[slotName] = containerName;\n    },\n\n    /*\n    position can be one of:\n     before = Werbebanner wird vor dem bestehenden Container platziert.\n     after = Werbebanner wird nach dem bestehenden Containers platziert.\n     attach = Werbebanner wird innerhalb des bestehenden Containers am Ende platziert.\n     prepend = Werbebanner wird innerhalb des bestehenden Container am Anfang platziert.\n     */\n    addAttachSlot : function(slotName, containerName, position){\n\n        var slotObj = {};\n        switch (position)\n        {\n            case \"attach\":\n                slotObj = {attach : containerName};\n                break;\n            case \"before\":\n                slotObj = {before : containerName};\n                break;\n            case \"prepand\":\n                slotObj = {prepand : containerName};\n                break;\n            case \"after\":\n                slotObj = {after : containerName};\n                break;\n            default:\n                slotObj = {attach : containerName};\n        }\n\n        this.slots[slotName] = slotObj;\n    },\n\n    addSlotCallback : function(callback){\n        if (typeof callback === \"function\")\n            this.slotCallback = callback;\n\n    },\n\n    addTag : function(tag){\n        this.tags.push(tag);\n    },\n\n    addCartProducts : function(cartProductsJsonArray){\n        for (var i in cartProductsJsonArray)\n        {\n            var product = cartProductsJsonArray[i];\n            if (product !== null\n                && typeof product === 'object')\n                this.cartProducts.push(product);\n        }\n    },\n\n    setIsCheckout : function(){\n        this.isCheckout = true;\n    },\n\n    send: function() {\n        var pageSettingsObj = {\n            cmd: \"setPageSettings\",\n            pageType: this.pageType,\n            products: this.products,\n            tags: this.tags,\n            mobileTagsOptions: this.mobileTags\n        };\n\n        if (Object.keys(this.sliderSlots).length > 0)\n        {\n            for (var name in this.sliderSlots)\n                this.slots[name] = this.sliderSlots[name];\n        }\n\n        var pageSlotsObj = {\n            cmd: \"setPageSlots\",\n            slots: this.slots\n        };\n        if (Object.keys(this.sliderSlots).length > 0)\n            this.loadBannerSlider();\n\n        if (this.slotCallback)\n            pageSlotsObj[\"callback\"] = this.slotCallback;\n\n        window.kias = window.kias || [];\n        window.kias.push(pageSettingsObj, pageSlotsObj);\n\n        if ( ! this.isCheckout && this.cartProducts.length > 0) {\n            window.kias.push(\n                {\n                    cmd: \"setCartProducts\",\n                    products: this.cartProducts\n                }\n            );\n        }\n\n        if (this.isCheckout) {\n            window.kias.push(\n                {\n                    cmd: \"checkout\",\n                    products: this.cartProducts\n                }\n            );\n        }\n\n    },\n\n    addBrandShopTag : function(brandName) {\n        this.addTag(\"kw_brand:\" + brandName);\n    },\n\n    addTopicShopTag : function(topicName) {\n        this.addTag(\"kw_topic:\" + topicName);\n    },\n\n    setSliderElementId : function(sliderElementId){\n        this.sliderElementId = sliderElementId;\n    },\n\n    addSliderSlot :function(slotName, customFunction) {\n\n        if (typeof customFunction == 'function')\n        {\n            this.sliderSlots[slotName] = customFunction;\n        }\n        else\n        {\n            this.sliderSlots[slotName] = function (url, size, slotId) {\n                var slider = $('#' + this.sliderElementId);\n                var sliderElement = '<div id=\"' + slotId + '\"><iframe width=\"' + size.w + '\" height=\"' + size.h + '\"  src=\"' + url + '\" ></iframe></div>';\n
